Day 10 @shirley_hunsberger … well I used to draw a lot of crystals in my pieces 😅 so I figured why not sketch one… I try to keep my sketch time nice and short - trying to loosen up so my art gets better … #dailysketch #sketchbook #artprocess #onedayatatime

This is the reason why I bid on Lots of items - by “Lots” I mean a large group of items… I feel I get more bang for my buck, you never now what you are going to get, and you have the possibility of finding a treasure! From the picture I saw there were several baskets and “wood things”… this purse was one of them… Then I get to research… this is most likely from the 1970’s… in fantastic condition- decoupage is still in great condition, no cracks, morrow inside is good and well attached - handle , hinges 👍🏼… it’s in my Etsy right now waiting for a new home!

Taught a painting class in town today… I sketched this from my students photo reference - all her photographs were her own - and all were beautiful! I would love to paint all of them lol but todays intention was to “teach” her to paint…. She was a great student - really the best teacher though is experience - just like with everything else in life - I can give tips and model some things I find useful… but the best thing is to just do it ❤️…. #art #artist #artwork #sketch #justdoit #artistsoninstagram #ivanavizart #ivanavizcarrondo
